{
  "texts": [
    "We organize the following subsections around a meta-analysis of our results across all models.",
    "For the model-specific observations or per-task discussion, please refer to Appendix F.3",
    "Table 2 shows that certain LMs consistently perform well on multiple taskse.g.",
    "DeepSeek R1 leads in many IR tasks and advanced QA settings, Claude 3.5 Sonnet excels in sentiment (FPB) and some IR tasks (FINRED), and GPT-4o hovers near the top in classification and summarization.",
    "Nevertheless, there was no single model that wins overall: while DeepSeek R1 dominates multi-step QA (e.g., CONVFINQA, TATQA), trails in summarization."
  ]
}